All features in the handout have been implemented:
		
	- Backing up directory
	- Creates a directory if it does not exists
	- Limiting backup to max-backups
	- Sending user an e-mail notification

To RUN:
	backup.sh <dir> <backupdir> <interval-secs> <max-backups>

Extra features:
	- Display usage example when the number of arguments is not 4
	- Show greeting when logout
